articles.title: Taylor Swift's dad, Scott, accused of assaulting paparazzi in Australia - Fox News
articles.description: Taylor Swift's father, Scott, has reportedly been accused of assaulting an Australian photographer early Tuesday morning. Swift's spokesperson explained the alleged situation to Fox News Digital.
